Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.80,0:03:11.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}库珀探员.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.94,0:03:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Cooper.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:14.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}能听见我说话么? 我是安迪阿.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.51,0:03:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me? It's Andy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.94,0:03:19.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}库珀探员, 我是安迪.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.04,0:03:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Cooper, it's Andy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.46,0:03:22.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}能听到我说话么?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.61,0:03:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.33,0:03:23.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}库珀探员?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.48,0:03:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Cooper?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.38,0:03:32.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你好,客房服务.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Room service.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.96,0:03:49.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你躺在那下面干嘛呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.07,0:03:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you doing down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.28,0:03:57.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,热奶来了.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:03:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Warm milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.84,0:03:59.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}库珀探员?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.98,0:03:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Cooper?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.67,0:04:04.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,请你把它放在桌子上,可以么?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you put it on the table, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.90,0:04:09.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 顺便帮我叫医生?\N- 乐意效劳.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.03,0:04:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- And would you call a doctor?\N- Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:12.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}你怎样了? 你能听见我么?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.80,0:04:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you aII right? Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.55,0:04:13.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}库珀探员.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.70,0:04:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Cooper.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:15.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}库珀探员.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.30,0:04:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Cooper.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.99,0:04:20.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}库珀探员, 我是安迪阿.\N你能听到我说话么?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.10,0:04:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Cooper, it's Andy.\NCan you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.39,0:04:23.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}你那边出什么事了?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.54,0:04:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you aII right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:26.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}库珀探员. 库珀探员.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.74,0:04:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Cooper. Agent Cooper.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:28.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}库珀探员.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.88,0:04:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Cooper.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:30.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我是安迪.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.02,0:04:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Andy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:34.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我是安...--{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's An--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.45,0:04:43.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你把电话挂了.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.60,0:04:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l hung it up for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.02,0:04:49.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.13,0:04:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.33,0:04:52.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,帮你把它挂了.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.44,0:04:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hung it up for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.59,0:04:56.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那你叫医生了没?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.74,0:04:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you call the doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:03.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,医生?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.85,0:05:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.56,0:05:08.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,挂了.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's hung up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.69,0:05:09.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那个电话.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.86,0:05:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.61,0:05:14.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.76,0:05:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.39,0:05:16.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是的.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:19.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.54,0:05:38.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,已经包括小费了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.68,0:05:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this include a gratuity?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.24,0:05:42.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是的,先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.39,0:05:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:56.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢,谢谢你这么大方.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. Thank you kindly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.44,0:06:09.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶要凉了.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.55,0:06:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The milk will get cool on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:13.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 很快就凉了.\N- 好的.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.78,0:06:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Pretty soon.\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.94,0:06:29.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我听说过你.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've heard about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.71,0:07:05.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我听说过你.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.87,0:07:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l heard about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:33.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我将给你3个暗示.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.59,0:08:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l will tell you three things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.01,0:08:38.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果它们都中了,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf l tell them to you\Nand they come true,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:41.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,到时候你会相信我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.27,0:08:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then will you believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.76,0:08:44.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.02,0:08:48.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,把我当作你的朋友.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think of me as a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:53.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你从哪里来?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.51,0:08:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.51,0:09:01.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不要问我从哪里来,\N应该问我将到哪里去?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.65,0:09:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The question is,\Nwhere have you gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.87,0:09:08.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我要给你的第一个暗示,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.99,0:09:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first thing l will tell you is,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.30,0:09:12.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.46,0:09:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's a man
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.35,0:09:15.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,躺在一个微笑的袋子里.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in a smiling bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.27,0:09:20.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,男人躺在一个微笑的袋子里.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man in a smiling bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:24.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,第二个暗示,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.91,0:09:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second thing is,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:29.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不要给猫头鹰的外表迷惑了.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.74,0:09:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the owls are not what they seem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.15,0:09:34.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,第三个暗示,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Third thing is,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.02,0:09:40.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,别给他用药, 他就会指引你.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.15,0:09:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without chemicals, he points.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:44.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你刚刚说的都是什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.83,0:09:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do these things mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.29,0:09:47.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我只能暗示你这些.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all l am permitted to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:50.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,把你的戒指给我.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me your ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:56.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当这些暗示都成真以后\N我会还给你的.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.67,0:09:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l will return it to you\Nwhen you find these things to be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.93,0:10:11.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们想帮助你.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.06,0:10:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.02,0:10:14.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,"我们"是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.16,0:10:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's ''we''?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.97,0:10:17.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还有最后一件事.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One last thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.93,0:10:23.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,里欧被锁在亨格力·豪斯里面.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.06,0:10:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leo locked inside hungry horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:26.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,线索就在里欧的亨格力·豪斯里面.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.80,0:10:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a clue at Leo's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.47,0:10:34.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你很快就会得到治疗.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will require medical attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.37,0:11:04.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我敲, 我敲, 我敲敲.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.51,0:11:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock, knock, knock.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.59,0:11:11.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,来呀.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.75,0:11:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.29,0:11:14.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,让我来看看你这新妞儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.42,0:11:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a look at the new girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.73,0:11:19.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢,辣妹.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vixen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.51,0:11:22.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,本杰明在哪间房?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.66,0:11:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What room is Ben in?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:28.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有小野花的那间.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.00,0:11:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The little flower room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:31.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他为什么要瞒着我?\N- 什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Why is he holding out on me?\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.48,0:11:35.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他为什么要瞒着我?\N- 你说什么, 布莱奇?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.64,0:11:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Why is he holding out on me?\N- What's that, Blackie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.87,0:11:39.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫「瞒着你」?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's holding out on who?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.88,0:11:43.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.02,0:11:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.49,0:11:46.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 布莱奇.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.65,0:11:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Blackie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.89,0:11:59.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你曾经是那么的漂亮.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.03,0:12:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You used to be so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.64,0:12:05.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,布莱奇, 布莱奇.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.80,0:12:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blackie, Blackie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.52,0:12:21.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.69,0:12:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:33.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你可以走了.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.07,0:12:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l think you should go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.41,0:12:37.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 真的, 想清楚了?\N- 嗯, 是的. 想的很清楚了.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.53,0:12:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Do you, Prudence?\N- Yes, l do. l really do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.24,0:12:41.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.37,0:12:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.20,0:12:44.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你坚持.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.34,0:12:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf you insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.65,0:13:06.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,逮到你了.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.83,0:13:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.13,0:13:10.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我要生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.27,0:13:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l will huff
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.61,0:13:12.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,怒火呼呼的吹,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.74,0:13:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and puff,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.09,0:13:17.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,把你的房顶吹翻.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.24,0:13:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and blow your house down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.75,0:13:20.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 宝贝, 宝贝.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.91,0:13:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:24.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.95,0:13:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.15,0:13:28.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我今天非的要看看你不可，把你看给逼真.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.29,0:13:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've got to see you. l must see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.02,0:13:33.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,走开啦. 好羞人.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.16,0:13:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go away. l'm shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:35.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,难道没有人告诉你我是谁吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.49,0:13:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't they tell you who l was?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.03,0:13:37.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,大老板?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.16,0:13:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The owner?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.03,0:13:40.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,完全正确.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.16,0:13:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:42.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,本, 我是哲.\N出了点状况.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ben, it's Jer.\NWe got a situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:46.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我这里也出了点状况.\N- 本哥, 别玩了，我们要去「干活」了.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- So have l.\N- Brother Ben, we got a S-N-A-G.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.00,0:13:50.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 阿莱丝, 我这会儿真的要走囉.\N- 快点, 本.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.14,0:13:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Alas, l do have a situation.\N- Come on, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.04,0:13:52.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,来了, 哲.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.18,0:13:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming, Jer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.65,0:13:54.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.78,0:13:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.79,0:13:58.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道怎样钩引男人.\N这样很重要.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:13:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know how to interest a man.\NThat's half the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.09,0:14:02.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,下次见,\N下次我们来玩点别的.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.25,0:14:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time,\Nwe will play a different game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.92,0:14:05.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我来订游戏规则.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.09,0:14:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll make the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.45,0:14:08.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你会喜欢的. 很好玩的.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.59,0:14:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll like it. Fun game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.93,0:14:13.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都会是赢家.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.10,0:14:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.79,0:14:53.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,戴安.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.94,0:14:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diane.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:58.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我的录音机在桌子上.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.71,0:14:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My recorder is on the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:03.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我够不着它.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.55,0:15:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm unable to reach it at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.76,0:15:07.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,只能希望\N我无意中按过那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can only hope\Nthat l inadvertently pressed
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.68,0:15:09.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,声控键.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.82,0:15:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the voice activation button.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.64,0:15:13.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在躺在房间的地板上.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm lying on the floor of my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.55,0:15:16.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我中枪了.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.69,0:15:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've been shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.30,0:15:21.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,剧痛\N还留了一大滩血.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.46,0:15:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a great deal of pain\Nand a fair amount of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.69,0:15:27.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,幸好, 从昨晚开始我一直穿着防弹背心,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.84,0:15:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunately, l was wearing\Nmy bulletproof vest last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.22,0:15:31.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,局里的规定\N执行任务时必须要穿.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.37,0:15:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,per bureau regulations\Nwhen working undercover.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.61,0:15:34.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我记得我把背心拉起来了一点,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l remember folding the vest up,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:37.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,想抓一只木蚤.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.75,0:15:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,trying to chase down a wood tick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.23,0:15:44.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你能想象吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.39,0:15:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf you can imagine the impact\Non your chest
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.32,0:15:48.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就像三个保龄球从九米高的地方砸下来一样,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.49,0:15:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of three bowling balls dropped\Nfrom a height of about 9 feet,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.24,0:15:52.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你可能已经开始在想象了吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.39,0:15:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you might begin\Nto approximate the sensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.46,0:15:58.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,仔细想想,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:15:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All things considered,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.33,0:16:03.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,其实中枪\N并不像我一直想象中那么糟糕.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.50,0:16:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,being shot is not as bad\Nas l always thought it might be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:06.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,只要你能保持住冷静，\N不要恐惧.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.71,0:16:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you can keep\Nthe fear from your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.34,0:16:13.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我猜你可能笑我\N「火星人都知道」.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.51,0:16:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But l guess you could say that\Nabout almost anything in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.30,0:16:18.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,真不像我想象中那么糟\N只要你能保持住冷静，不要恐惧.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's not so bad as long as you can keep\Nthe fear from your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.10,0:16:32.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 天啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.24,0:16:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.23,0:16:34.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我的戒指不见了.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.41,0:16:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ring is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.46,0:16:46.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在这种时候不见了, 太奇怪了,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.62,0:16:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At a time like this, curiously,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.20,0:16:49.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我开始\N为自己感到很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.32,0:16:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you begin to think\Nof the things you regret
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.95,0:16:52.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,遗憾那些我错过的事.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.09,0:16:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or the things you might miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.56,0:16:59.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我很想...总之, 我希望在有生之年\N能尽量多关心他人，并以礼相待.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.69,0:16:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l would like, in general, to treat people\Nwith much more care and respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.48,0:17:03.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我还想去登山，登很高的山.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.63,0:17:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l would like to climb a tall hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.87,0:17:06.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,也别太高.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not too tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.27,0:17:08.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,想坐在凉凉的绿草地上.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.44,0:17:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sit in the cool grass.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.05,0:17:11.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,也别太凉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.18,0:17:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not too cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.27,0:17:14.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一边感受洒在脸上的温暖阳光.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.38,0:17:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And feel the sun on my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.88,0:17:20.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我还希望可以破了\N灵博格的那个绑票案.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.02,0:17:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l wish l could have cracked\Nthe Lindbergh kidnapping case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.32,0:17:25.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的希望\N和一个美人儿做爱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.49,0:17:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l would very much like\Nto make love to a beautiful woman
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.89,0:17:29.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一个我真心爱的美人儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.03,0:17:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who l had genuine affection for.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.64,0:17:36.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,啊还有, 还用说么?\N我还要去西藏.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.80,0:17:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And of course, it goes without saying\Nthat l would like to visit Tibet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.21,0:17:41.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我盼望着西藏人民能重获他们的家园\N达赖喇嘛也能重回家乡.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.34,0:17:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l wish they could get their country back\Nand the Dalai Lama could return.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.69,0:17:44.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 太多东西想做了.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.84,0:17:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, l would like that very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.83,0:17:51.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之,\N这次是个很有意思的体验.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.98,0:17:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All in all,\Na very interesting experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.23,0:18:00.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们终于来了.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.36,0:18:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:09.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我的皮肤好痒.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.23,0:18:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My skin was itching.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.89,0:18:13.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当时有一只木跳蚤在爬.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.04,0:18:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wood tick was crawling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.11,0:18:17.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,于是我就提起防弹背心.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l lifted my bulletproof vest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.29,0:18:19.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,三下重击.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.41,0:18:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three slugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.81,0:18:22.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,近距离开枪.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.95,0:18:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Point-blank range.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.47,0:18:23.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你看这个.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.58,0:18:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That explains this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.43,0:18:29.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,倒霉的木跳蚤，给打得稀巴烂.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.55,0:18:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell of a way to kill a tick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.78,0:18:34.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你看到那个持枪歹徒的脸了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.93,0:18:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get a look at the gunman?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.87,0:18:43.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,只看到了面具, 和枪口的火光.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.03,0:18:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l saw a masked face, muzzle flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.10,0:18:51.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,露西, 你最好给库珀探员\N汇报一下今天的情况.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.24,0:18:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, you better bring Agent Cooper\Nup-to-date.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.02,0:18:56.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,里欧·强生中枪了.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.18,0:18:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leo Johnson was shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.24,0:18:58.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,雅克·雷诺被勒死了.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:18:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jacques Renault was strangled.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.67,0:19:02.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,锯木厂被烧燬了.\N雪莉和皮特给浓烟熏倒了.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:19:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mill burned.\NShelly and Pete got smoke inhalation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.59,0:19:04.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,凯萨琳和乔西都失了踪.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.76,0:19:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catherine and Josie are missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.90,0:19:08.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,纳丁服食过量安眠药\N现在昏迷中.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.06,0:19:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nadine is in a coma\Nfrom taking sleeping pills.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.29,0:19:16.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 已经几点了?\N- 早晨7:45了.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.43,0:19:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- How long have l been out?\N- lt's 7:45 in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.73,0:19:18.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,整晚\N暂时都没什么动静
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't had this much action\Nin one night
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.00,0:19:21.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,只有59区的角鹿社俱乐部失火了.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.14,0:19:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since the Elk's Club fire of '59.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.56,0:19:27.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里, 我们要申请搜查令\N去搜查里欧·强生的房子.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.71,0:19:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry, we need to get a search warrant\Nfor Leo Johnson's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.70,0:19:31.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了. 里欧就在\N自己的客厅中枪的.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No need. Leo was shot\Nin his own living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.83,0:19:35.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是戴佩提·布伦南发现他的.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.98,0:19:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deputy Brennan found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.62,0:19:43.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你那儿都不能去.\N- 医生. 当正义在召唤的时候,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.76,0:19:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You're not going anywhere.\N- Doc. When the will is invoked,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:47.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,身体的复原能力\N会变得非常惊人.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.10,0:19:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the recuperative powers of the physical\Nbody are simply extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.38,0:19:57.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,只需要给我几个小时\N换衣服.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.51,0:19:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give me a couple of hours\Nto get dressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.44,0:20:15.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我现在正站在\N一大片的贮木场前{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm standing just in front of\Nwhere a massive Iog-storage area
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.26,0:20:17.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}帕卡德锯木厂\N被大火烧成一片废墟,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.39,0:20:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the Packard Saw MiII\Nburned to the ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.05,0:20:20.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}消防局的调查员\N在彻底调查后声称这次是一个{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.20,0:20:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,under what fire department\Ninvestigators are caIIing
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.14,0:20:22.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"神秘事件. "{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.30,0:20:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,''mysterious circumstances. ''
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.19,0:20:27.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}迄今为止, 这是我们能从官方\N所获得的最多消息,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.34,0:20:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, poIice officiaIs have toId me\Nthat they have, as of yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.15,0:20:30.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}- 波比.\N- 所获证据表明{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.31,0:20:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Bobby.\N- uncovered no apparent Iink
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.71,0:20:32.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}这两个事件之间\N似乎没有直接的关系{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.84,0:20:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,between these two\NseemingIy unreIated
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.76,0:20:34.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}- 波比.\N- 很可能只是两个不幸的意外.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.88,0:20:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Bobby.\N- tragedies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.37,0:20:36.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}这里是帕卡德锯木厂\N现场为你直播...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.51,0:20:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reporting Iive\Nfrom the Packard Saw MiII...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.89,0:20:39.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,库珀, 你不能这样走\N完全不顾自己的身体.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.05,0:20:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cooper, this is totally\Nagainst my recommendations.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.64,0:20:41.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没事, 医生. 我会小心的.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.79,0:20:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's all right, doc. Duly noted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.33,0:20:43.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你断了两条肋骨,\N好些小软骨还没修复.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.49,0:20:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got two busted ribs,\Nyour cartilage is a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.99,0:20:46.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,天知道还会发生什么事故?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.16,0:20:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows what else is wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.69,0:20:49.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.83,0:20:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.82,0:20:52.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,雅克·雷诺.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.00,0:20:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jacques Renault.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.13,0:20:55.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得那个袋子在微笑吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.30,0:20:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls that bag smiling?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.09,0:20:59.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,微笑?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.24,0:20:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smiling?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.48,0:21:03.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,都这时候了,还有什么好微笑的?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.61,0:21:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's there to smile about?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.22,0:22:32.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你想念贝丝吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.40,0:22:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you miss Beth?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.74,0:22:34.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.90,0:22:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.31,0:22:38.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你想念你妈妈吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.47,0:22:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been missing your mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.53,0:22:46.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 莎拉姨妈?\N- 嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.68,0:22:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Aunt Sarah?\N- Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.45,0:22:48.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我昨天晚上作了个怪梦.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.61,0:22:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l had the strangest dream last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.28,0:22:51.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,什么怪梦?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.45,0:22:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.28,0:22:57.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,梦见了地毯.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.45,0:22:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rug.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.50,0:22:58.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就在这里.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.66,0:22:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.33,0:23:02.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,从这里\N我正坐着这里.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.49,0:23:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right from this angle\Nwhere l'm sitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.64,0:23:04.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你梦见到劳拉了?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.80,0:23:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was Laura in it?
