Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.25,0:23:55.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 利兰.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.38,0:23:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Leland.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.77,0:23:57.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,利兰姨父的头发都变白了.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.91,0:23:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle Leland's hair turned white.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.04,0:24:00.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,利兰, 回来.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.18,0:24:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leland, come back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.32,0:24:23.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 天啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.44,0:24:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.50,0:24:30.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,来. 日程表.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.65,0:24:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Agenda.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.02,0:24:32.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,第一.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.15,0:24:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.89,0:24:34.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我要知道凯萨琳现在是死是活.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.05,0:24:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want a location on Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.85,0:24:38.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们装作什么都不知道,\N她来做替罪羊.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.02,0:24:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep our distance, just make sure\Nshe's ready to take the fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.99,0:24:40.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,第二.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.12,0:24:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.47,0:24:42.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我要知道\N里欧·强生的详细病情
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.63,0:24:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want a complete medical\Non Leo Johnson
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.90,0:24:44.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看他到底有没康复的迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.06,0:24:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his prospects for recovery
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.69,0:24:48.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我还要汉克·詹宁斯\N好好给我解释
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.83,0:24:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a satisfactory explanation\Nfrom Hank Jennings
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.47,0:24:52.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么在格斯伍纪念公园的时候\N里欧没有被警察捉去做酒精测验呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.63,0:24:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why Leo isn't being measured\Nfor a plot in Ghostwood Memorial Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.91,0:24:55.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样，有好开始就已经成功一半了.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.07,0:24:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well begun is half done.
