Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.94,1:22:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aces.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.76,1:22:47.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,漫漫长日, 难熬吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.28,1:22:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long day, Will?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.59,1:22:55.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉就像坐在那儿听\N一部老掉牙的冗长歌剧.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.11,1:22:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l feel like l've sat through\Nback-to-back operas.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.12,1:22:59.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在医学院读书时, 我们就学会了\N一天只睡几个小时或者只打个盹.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.62,1:22:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ln med school, we learned to live\Non three hours a night and cat naps.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.64,1:23:01.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,锯木厂发生的事实在太可怕了.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.16,1:23:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's terrible about the mill.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.90,1:23:05.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊. 报道说\N将近150人因此而失业.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.42,1:23:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. They say more\Nthan 1 50 jobs may be lost.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.38,1:23:07.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,太吓人了. 真实太吓人了.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.89,1:23:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awful. Just awful.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.95,1:23:10.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但有人欢喜有人愁啊
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.46,1:23:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l suppose this will open the door
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.87,1:23:15.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,对本·荷恩的发展大计来说\N就是天大的喜讯.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.40,1:23:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for Ben Horne\Nand his big development plans.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.00,1:23:18.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 我同时是你和他两个人的律师,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.51,1:23:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, as his lawyer, and yours,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.66,1:23:21.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,对此我还是不做评论的好.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.17,1:23:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of course l can't comment.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.70,1:23:25.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那好, 同时我也是你的医生, 利兰,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.24,1:23:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, as your doctor, Leland,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.19,1:23:27.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你的白头发到底是怎么搞的?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.68,1:23:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what the hell happened to your hair?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.54,1:23:31.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪, 是吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.02,1:23:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt is strange, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.06,1:23:33.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,唔, 我只是...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.59,1:23:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, l just...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.37,1:23:36.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我一觉醒来,\N在镜子里就发现自己这样了.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.89,1:23:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l woke up this morning,\Nlooked in the mirror and there it was.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.50,1:23:38.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,真是一夜白了少年头啊
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.99,1:23:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt had literally changed overnight.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.94,1:23:41.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 仔细想想\N你最近经历的事也够...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.46,1:23:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, considering\Nall you've been through...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.59,1:23:43.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗, 有趣的是,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.10,1:23:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, the funny thing about it is,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.73,1:23:46.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看看, 我已经意识到无论如何
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.27,1:23:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,seeing it, l realized that l had
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.90,1:23:49.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,要坚强起来，靠自己熬过去.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.44,1:23:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,turned a corner somehow.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.56,1:23:52.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，尽管我现在\N还是如此沉痛,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.04,1:23:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l feel a great deal\Nof sadness still, yes,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.78,1:23:55.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不能任由它把我压垮.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.31,1:23:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it wasn't as overwhelming to me.
