Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.45,1:24:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l physically felt as if a great weight\Nhad been lifted from my heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.09,1:24:03.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 希望是吧.\N- 希望是吧.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.62,1:24:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Perhaps it has.\N- Perhaps it has.
