Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.93,1:25:54.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,黛安, 现在晚上11:55了,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.43,1:25:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diane, it's 1 1 :55 p.m.,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.63,1:25:57.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我中枪后已经\N持续工作19个小时了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.13,1:25:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,approximately 1 9 hours\Nsince the shooting incident
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.33,1:25:59.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我几乎萌生了\N要归隐田园
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.83,1:26:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which nearly caused me\Nto make a premature purchase
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.81,1:26:01.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,的念头.
