Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.20,1:26:04.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在累得像狗一样.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.74,1:26:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm dog-tired.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.38,1:26:08.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,原来一个人\N可以极限到这种程度.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.91,1:26:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man can only go so long\Nwithout submitting to a period of rest.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.90,1:26:10.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,按照美军
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.41,1:26:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For as we know from experiments
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.64,1:26:13.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在朝鲜战争时\N的经验教训,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.15,1:26:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,conducted on American Gls\Nduring the Korean War,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.86,1:26:18.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,睡眠权利被剥夺后\N绝对会导致间歇性精神病.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.35,1:26:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,sleep deprivation is a one-way ticket\Nto temporary psychosis.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.52,1:26:21.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得自己已经成了工作狂了.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.05,1:26:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And l'm working on a three-day jag.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.35,1:26:24.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我昨晚多傻吗, 黛安,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.86,1:26:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l got so goofy last night, Diane,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.22,1:26:27.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我躺在地上时开始在想\N我是想死呢，还是想活呢,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.76,1:26:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lying here wondering\Nwhether l was going to live or die,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.53,1:26:31.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,然后我看见了\N一个巨人出现在我房间里.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.06,1:26:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that l thought l saw\Na giant in my room.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.75,1:26:35.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，这个事\N还是下次再说吧.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.27,1:26:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or perhaps that's a story\Nl'll save for another time.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.06,1:26:38.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我是, 戴尔,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.57,1:26:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is me, Dale,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.19,1:26:42.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,大北方酒店315房,\N完毕.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.71,1:26:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,room 31 5 at The Great Northern Hotel,\Nsigning off.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.52,1:27:08.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,特派探员.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.04,1:27:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special agent.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.05,1:27:13.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,特派探员. 特派探员.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.54,1:27:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special agent. Special agent.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.27,1:27:19.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,特派探员, 你听到吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.81,1:27:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special agent, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.15,1:27:26.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我给你留了言.\N你收到我留的纸条了吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.65,1:27:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l left you a note.\NDidn't you get my note?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.02,1:27:31.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我把它从门缝里塞进去了.\N保佑你一定要看到它.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.52,1:27:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l slipped it under your door.\NYou must have seen it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.51,1:27:42.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 我在这儿呢\N单眼杰克赌场.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.04,1:27:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, l'm up here\Nat One-Eyed Jack's.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.73,1:27:47.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,说真的,\N我想我这次搞的有点过火了.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.24,1:27:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be perfectly honest,\Nl think l'm in a little over my head.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.30,1:27:53.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,已经超过了我的能力范围.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.85,1:27:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that l can't handle it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.61,1:27:57.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说, 其实我只想帮你\N破案,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.15,1:27:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l mean, if l'm gonna help you out\Nwith your investigations,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.70,1:28:00.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在的情形\N比我原来想象的要危险的多
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.22,1:28:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sure l'll be put into situations\Na lot more dangerous than this
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.79,1:28:03.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我所能控制的了.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.29,1:28:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on a fairly regular basis.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.10,1:28:07.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.59,1:28:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's just...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.06,1:28:11.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...你要明白, 尽管这是我头一次出远门.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.56,1:28:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you know, my first time out.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.84,1:28:14.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我也事先作了一些准备的.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.37,1:28:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l could use a little expert guidance.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.33,1:28:20.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,所以，你知道我已经查到什么了,\N荷恩百货大厦
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.81,1:28:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you know,\Nthere is a connection
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.11,1:28:23.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,和单眼杰克赌场\N原来都是一伙的.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.61,1:28:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,between Horne's Department Store\Nand One-Eyed Jack's.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.77,1:28:26.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是我爸爸, 两个地方都是属于他的.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.28,1:28:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's my father, he owns the place.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.99,1:28:29.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那个胆小鬼马屁精经理巴蒂斯\N负责从香水柜台
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.48,1:28:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little ball of sleaze named Battis\Nhelps to recruit some of the girls
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.12,1:28:32.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,招募新的女孩子.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.62,1:28:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from the perfume counter.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.08,1:28:36.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,明天我会再去查查看\N劳拉和朗尼特是不是也给招进来过.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.59,1:28:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow l'm gonna try to find out\Nif Laura and Ronette came up here.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.70,1:28:47.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我只希望你不会觉得\N我为你做的这些事微不足道.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.23,1:28:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l hope you won't think any less of me\Nfor trying to help you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.61,1:28:52.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你明白吗, 我只为了你\N才会做这些事的.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.14,1:28:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, l promise l only did it\Nwith the best of intentions.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.92,1:28:56.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,所以，如果...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.44,1:28:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if there's any way...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.75,1:29:01.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果现在你在世界的某处\N听见了我的求救声,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.28,1:29:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf there's any way in the world\Nthat you can hear me right now,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.98,1:29:04.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就请快来救救我吧.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.48,1:29:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,please help me.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.67,1:29:08.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,救我. 救我.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.22,1:29:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me. Help me.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.85,1:29:55.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉把你吵醒了.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.37,1:29:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to wake you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.72,1:30:00.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是做梦吧.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.27,1:30:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l am not dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.38,1:30:03.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有件事我忘记告诉你了.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.88,1:30:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l forgot to tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.55,1:30:08.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那个微笑的袋子\N你的暗示中了.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.05,1:30:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were right\Nabout the smiling bag.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.08,1:30:12.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我给你的暗示\N不会错的.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.58,1:30:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The things l tell you\Nwill not be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.83,1:30:18.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，现在听我说.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.36,1:30:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Better to listen than to talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.31,1:30:21.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.83,1:30:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l believe you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.09,1:30:25.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不要急于\N一次得到所有的答案.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.60,1:30:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't search\Nfor all the answers at once.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.27,1:30:31.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,万事有道，一切都安排好了\N只需一步一脚印的走下去.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.80,1:30:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A path is formed\Nby laying one stone at a time.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.36,1:30:40.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有一个人看见了神秘人.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.88,1:30:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One person saw the third man.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.20,1:30:44.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,见过3次, 是的,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.72,1:30:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three have seen him, yes,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.50,1:30:46.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不仅仅是他的肉身.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.02,1:30:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but not his body.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.59,1:30:50.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一个你认识的人.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.09,1:30:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One only known to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.90,1:30:52.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他已经准备好了，就等你去问.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.43,1:30:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready now to talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.17,1:30:58.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还有一件事.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.70,1:30:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.95,1:31:01.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你忘东西了.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.47,1:31:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You forgot something.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.65,1:31:05.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.14,1:31:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.21,1:32:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laura! Laura!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.72,1:32:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laura!
